md:note.div:
De første 9 mongolske eventyr ud af 16 fra Tsakhar. På foranledning af Kaare Grønbech (1901-1957) blev de fremsagt af Lhabsurungjab (en dreng fra Tsakhar) og en mand ved navn Tončoy og nedskrevet af Lhabsurungjab og Tamirinsürüng in vinteren 1938/39.
Værkerne er beskrevet i: Catalogue of Mongol Books, Manuscripts and Xylographs by Walter Heissig assisted by Charles Bawden, The Royal Library, Copenhagen 1971 pp. 33-38.
Mong. 406a-i

The first 9 folktales out of 16 from Tsakhar. On the request of Kaare Grønbech (1901-1957) during the winter of 1938/39 they were oral told by Lhabsurungjab (a Tsakhar boy) and Tončoy and noted down by Lhabsurungjab og Tamirinsürüng.
The collection is described in: Catalogue of Mongol Books, Manuscripts and Xylographs by Walter Heissig assisted by Charles Bawden, The Royal Library, Copenhagen 1971 pp. 33-38.
Mong. 406a-i
